abstract: This talk will explore how Python can be leveraged to build robust DDoS defense mechanisms, focusing on real-time threat detection, mitigation strategies, and system resilience. We will dive into key Python libraries, best practices, and techniques to protect your applications from large-scale DDoS attacks while ensuring high availability.
